text: Kurorta () is a rural locality (a selo) in Gafuriysky District, Krasnoulsky Selsoviet, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 598 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Krasnousolsky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Kurorta
